<section class='tool-section bg-tool-orange'>
  <div class="tool connect-tool">
    <div class='info-section'>
      <h2 class='q-h2'>Quill Connect</h2>
      <p class='blurb'>Help your students advance from fragmented and run-on sentences to complex and well structured ones.</p>
        <div class="light-bar"></div>
      <p class='summary'>
        Using the evidence-based strategy of sentence combining, students combine multiple ideas into a single sentence. They then receive instant feedback designed to help them improve their clarity and precision.
